World,Addresses,is,an,address,validation,and,data,management,solution,for,companies,dealing,with,large,amounts,of,customer,mailing,data,The,API,allows,users,to,conduct,searches,to,lookup,address,data,using,a,number,of,parameters,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,or,JSON,Full,documentation,is,available,upon,registration